{"tid":830071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港租深圳灣口岸要咁多錢，中国租西九龍就每年1000?","createTime":"2018-09-21T02:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T04:48:57.000Z","uid":147376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f324441f9f9a47b4f5b464074986549e5b0d45","tid":830071,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T02:27:56.000Z","msg":"香港與深圳為深圳灣口岸港方口岸區簽訂租約，土地使用期限至<span style=\"color: red;\">2047年6月30日</span>，自啟用起港方<span style=\"color: red;\">每年需付逾623萬元人民幣（810萬港幣）</span>租金予深圳市政府。<span style=\"color: red;\">租金每5年調整一次，調整幅度上限為30%。</span>而此等土地租借模式亦於之後的澳門大學新校區中應用。<br />\n此外，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港還需要向內地支付17.2億人民幣的「土地開發費」</span>，因此有泛民議員要求港府向中央政府收取高鐵西九龍站「土地開發費」。<span style=\"color: red;\">到2018年，因應《廣深港高鐵（一地兩檢）條例》刊憲，深圳國土局將於2019年7月1日起將深圳灣口岸下調至每年1000元人民幣的象徵式租金。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/深圳灣口岸\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%81%A3%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8&d=SYfG%2FrpWfShsoGytOeV0sXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c8009d35\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/深圳灣口岸</a>"},{"pid":"3895008bf176a63979d81d49c4738dfe02b3f5f4","tid":830071,"uid":7004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T02:42:39.000Z","msg":"因為大陸一直想食我地呢舊肥豬肉"},{"pid":"567b452519ab40262d4fad588288e16008f1f60d","tid":830071,"uid":211145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"自己用自己嘢，唔洗計得甘清楚喇"},{"pid":"72ff5338824b135bcfe63dc9a5999a1c45a9fcd1","tid":830071,"uid":13160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"擺明送錢上去，咁點？"},{"pid":"00d2923df88b70e3451442c8fe08a460b04b0623","tid":830071,"uid":101390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"因為香港係中國殖民地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}